{"tid":1507211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有一種人係唔會醒覺","createTime":"2019-08-26T05:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T05:19:03.000Z","uid":260253,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"666d2fb48728e85f06dafa941db003ed1f3ce63c","tid":1507211,"uid":260253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"個種就係廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴晚阿叔跪地叫黑警唔好開槍<br />\n阿叔既勇氣同行為令作為年輕人既我都感到慚愧<br />\n但今日返工竟然聽到廢老話個阿叔跪地係有陰謀<br />\n隨時會捉住個黑警隻腳，攻擊黑警<br />\n仲話阿叔收左錢先會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以真係唔好怪香港社會仇老<br />\n黃藍我當係政見不同，各有取向<br />\n但連良心都冇<br />\n根本枉為人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2c721da5dbdb19da44d0a457c63a7a94e623a5","tid":1507211,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:19:03.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjbVjJ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjbVjJ3.jpg&h=4677b5e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=a0977980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DhSUAso.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDhSUAso.jpg&h=aaca1d02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=a0977980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"}]}